lead_paragraph: Evergreen Catriona Matthew, boosted by having husband Graham back on her bag after a spell looking after their two young children, launched a determined title charge at the Ricoh Women's British Open on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Best-Of-The-Day 65 Sends Matthew Soaring at Woburn
